nudge

nudge is a chrome extension designed to help students and employees stay on track while browsing the net.

General Info:
Our current website: nudge.carrd.co
Our current chrome extension page: https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/nudge/hnlfpbcpjlpcpelnjehoggfhbkjclnlh
This was developed by Max Albert and Ben Freiband. Two juniors at the University of Michigan studying computer science.

What you can learn from this project:
This project uses a variety of google webkit api features such as:
Google.notifcations
Google.timer
Google.url

Installation:
1. Download the zip file
2. Unzip it
3. Unload the folder to any chrome browser
